Sohini Sengupta Halder in and as Bappaditya

 Bappaditya

 Nandikar adapts the popular story by Abanindranath Tagore with Sohini Sengupta Halder in the lead. She plays Bappaditya, the three princesses he is enamoured of and the narrator. Directed by Goutam Halder.

Catch it at Academy of Fine Arts, 6.30 pm, July 

